  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to wishlist and follow!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179280/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1738948712\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179280/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1738948712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179280/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1738948712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT FRIENDLY SHEEPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Friendly Sheeps is a relaxing sheep farming game that includes some Crafting and Business Management elements with its simple gameplay. Meet the needs of your sheepies, craft and sell your products, grow your business and unlock every corner of your farm!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RELAX BY TAKING CARE OF YOUR SHEEPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sheeps are your most valuable asset. Harvest crops to feed them! Keep your sheep happy and they will give you milk, wool, and more in return.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT AND SELL YOUR PRODUCTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft the most profitable products with your assets then sell them. Invest your profits in your business again by purchasing some automation or new structures to make new recipes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RAISE YOUR FRIENDLY SHEEPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 3 days, your Friendly Sheepies will want to make a baby sheepy. More sheepies means more products, more products means more profit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BE PART OF OUR FRIENDLY SHEEPS FAMILY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add Friendly Sheeps to your wishlist, follow us, and join our discord community so you don't miss out on any news!</p></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to wishlist and follow!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179280/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1738948712\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179280/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1738948712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179280/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1738948712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT FRIENDLY SHEEPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Friendly Sheeps is a relaxing sheep farming game that includes some Crafting and Business Management elements with its simple gameplay. Meet the needs of your sheepies, craft and sell your products, grow your business and unlock every corner of your farm!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RELAX BY TAKING CARE OF YOUR SHEEPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sheeps are your most valuable asset. Harvest crops to feed them! Keep your sheep happy and they will give you milk, wool, and more in return.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT AND SELL YOUR PRODUCTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft the most profitable products with your assets then sell them. Invest your profits in your business again by purchasing some automation or new structures to make new recipes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RAISE YOUR FRIENDLY SHEEPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 3 days, your Friendly Sheepies will want to make a baby sheepy. More sheepies means more products, more products means more profit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BE PART OF OUR FRIENDLY SHEEPS FAMILY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add Friendly Sheeps to your wishlist, follow us, and join our discord community so you don't miss out on any news!</p>",
